Privacy Policy for FlashLight Pro

Effective Date: March 26, 2025

At FlashLight Pro, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application.

1. Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information or use third-party services that require personal data. The app functions solely as a flashlight and does not request access to any personal information, such as your name, email, or location.

However, certain data may be automatically collected by your device, such as:

Device information

Usage data (such as app interaction, settings, etc.)


This information is used solely to improve the app’s functionality and user experience.

2. How We Use Your Information

The information collected is used solely for the following purposes:

To improve app performance.

To enhance your user experience.


3. Data Security

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect the information we collect. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

4. Third-Party Services

FlashLight Pro does not integrate any third-party services that collect personal information.

5. Your Choices

You have the option to disable app permissions, such as camera or location, in your device settings. However, disabling certain permissions may affect the functionality of the app.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be communicated within the app and the revised Privacy Policy will be posted on this page with the updated effective date.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

